USER_INVITE.BODY:
You're receiving this email because an account was created for you at {{siteUrl}}.

To complete your profile and set a password, open the following link in your browser: {{resetUrl}}

You can safely ignore this message if you do not wish to complete the account creation process.

FORGOT_PASSWORD.BODY:
You're receiving this email because you entered your email address and clicked the forgot password link at {{siteUrl}}.

To reset your password, open the following link in your browser: {{resetUrl}}

You can safely ignore this message if you do not wish to reset your password.

USER_RESET.BODY:
You're receiving this email because your account was reset by an administrator at {{siteUrl}}.

To recover your account and set a new password, open the following link in your browser: {{resetUrl}}

You can safely ignore this message if you do not wish to recover your account.
